<span id="freeTextContainer5605129857405509362">While pursuing his quest for the Dark Tower through a world that is a nightmarishly distorted mirror image of our own, Roland, the last gunslinger, encounters three mysterious doorways on the beach. Each one enters into the life of a different person living in contemporary New York. <br/><br/>Here he links forces with the defiant young Eddie Dean and the beautiful, brilliant, and br</span>
  <span id="freeText5605129857405509362" style="display:none">While pursuing his quest for the Dark Tower through a world that is a nightmarishly distorted mirror image of our own, Roland, the last gunslinger, encounters three mysterious doorways on the beach. Each one enters into the life of a different person living in contemporary New York. <br /><br />Here he links forces with the defiant young Eddie Dean and the beautiful, brilliant, and brave Odetta Holmes, in a savage struggle against underworld evil and otherworldly enemies.<br /><br />Once again, Stephen King has masterfully interwoven dark, evocative fantasy and icy realism.</span>
