  <span id="freeText12467608271381639432" style="display:none"><p>Just not my kind of book or series I guess.</p><p>I found some parts interesting but having to dig through the paragraph-long sentences that seemed to jump randomly from subject to subject just lost me. </p><p>Some people really enjoyed this book. I've had many people recommend it. I passed the 50% mark today, which is my rule before giving up on a book, and decided I simply was NOT enjoying it at all and saw no point in continuing.  </p><p>I'm really disappointed because I had heard so many good things about this series. </p><br /></span>
